{"tid":558790,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"老母比d推銷員呃錢","createTime":"2018-02-12T14:42:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-13T02:56:08.000Z","uid":139792,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8ba07c10565c1b49065db26dc035d238feedd440","tid":558790,"uid":139792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T14:42:06.000Z","msg":"話說小妹身體比較差，於是老母會間唔中買d補品翻嚟比我食<br />\n但我成日都叫老母唔好曬錢買，屋企又唔係有錢，而且有d食完都唔覺有好轉<br />\n然後老母話見我近期成日都捱夜，身體唔好啊乜乜乜<br />\n之後就係唔知邊到買左呢盒乜鳩人參粉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/12/222625_18f7a3e462343bcf33d75c126e97a832.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F12%2F222625_18f7a3e462343bcf33d75c126e97a832.jpeg&h=6821bae5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我見到個包裝已經覺得唔對路，覺得好中國feel，但佢寫住台灣做<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後呢罐嘢仲送左本說明書咁嘅物體<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/12/222954_c2ff591212b47fe4c3aacd61a0eec5d7.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F12%2F222954_c2ff591212b47fe4c3aacd61a0eec5d7.jpeg&h=a69399e7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/12/222957_52d031c80f3c2f63ba6a9fd5b48fe9e0.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F12%2F222957_52d031c80f3c2f63ba6a9fd5b48fe9e0.jpeg&h=5528d34f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n睇完之後心諗wtf呢罐嘢實係可以能醫百病啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟住問埋老母呢罐嘢買左幾錢<br />\n老母話買左$1600<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我諗住罐嘢$300左右咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後仲要比我上網搵到呢間嘢有前科，新聞有講呢罐嘢農藥超標，會影響肝功能同中樞神經<br />\n我同老母講呢單新聞之後老母話上網個d假㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n叫我試左先，唔得先算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n求救我可以點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b922c009b7954645ac59cf15f9c7f8f8e6f19235","tid":558790,"uid":163554,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T14:51:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0b4e6420cb648f43d4d75be0ad16b9bbeecc4bf5","tid":558790,"uid":103380,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T14:51:15.000Z","msg":"唔食 <br />\n上網睇到會食壞人仲擺入口？<br />\n買左一罐當買個教訓 <br />\n<br />\n叫你老母不如正正經經去大鋪頭買返啲正當人參仲好"},{"pid":"653420c215f2848c770e81b000335e4e351d69c7","tid":558790,"uid":49004,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T15:15:28.000Z","msg":"呢個世界啲老母都係自以為是懶醒的on9"},{"pid":"354cdc3db4064dfe43ad815f240461af71014bf0","tid":558790,"uid":36478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T19:12:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7613958a5ec0bfe791195fcee5c8f2218239fdac","tid":558790,"uid":7854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T19:25:17.000Z","msg":"睇樓主D文筆肯定帶眼鏡 肥底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c672c503a7e7b4367fe8062169ecc390f93a9c2c","tid":558790,"uid":39825,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T02:56:08.000Z","msg":"層壓式推銷？<br />\n問埋你老母有冇人叫佢做埋買賣"}]}